---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Kilimanjaro Pilot Offer | Hoogly"
	description="Special pilot offer for organisations that care deeply about culture and employee wellbeing. Support Pam's Kilimanjaro climb while transforming your workplace."
	type="website"
>
	<section style="padding: 0; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;">
		<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
			<h1 style="font-size: 2.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #222; font-family: 'Outfit', var(--font-family-heading); margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0; line-height: 1.5;">
				<span style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">Terms & Conditions</span><br>
				<span style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">(The Friendly Version)</span>
			</h1>
		</div>
		<div style="height: 2.5rem;"></div>
		<div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
			<div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); backdrop-filter: blur(16px); border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 3rem; box-shadow: none; border: none;">
				<div style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
					Thanks for your interest in the <strong>Hoogly x Forever Projects</strong> pilot offer! Before we get started, here are a few things to keep in mind:
				</div>

				<div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
					<h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
						<span style="color: #3bb273; font-size: 1.2rem;">✅</span> Who's eligible?
					</h2>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
						This offer is for organisations that care deeply about culture and employee wellbeing. We're starting with <strong>10 companies</strong> — but we may extend that number if it helps maximise the impact (and support Pam's incredible Kilimanjaro climb!).
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
					<h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
						<span style="color: #3bb273; font-size: 1.2rem;">🐣</span> We're early — and that's part of the magic
					</h2>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
						Hoogly is growing fast, and this pilot is part of our journey. In return for this special offer, we ask that you be open, patient, and willing to share honest feedback to help us improve the experience.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
					<h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
						<span style="color: #3bb273; font-size: 1.2rem;">📅</span> When can you start?
					</h2>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
						You can begin anytime in <strong>August, September, or October 2025</strong> — just let us know what works best for your team.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
					<h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
						<span style="color: #3bb273; font-size: 1.2rem;">👥</span> What if you have more than 100 employees?
					</h2>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
						No worries — the first 100 people are included in the $100 offer. If you'd like to include more, you can easily top up at <strong>AU$8 per person per month</strong>.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
					<h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
						<span style="color: #3bb273; font-size: 1.2rem;">📦</span> What's included?
					</h2>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
						You'll get access to everything in our Standard Package, including:
					</div>
					<ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; color: #222; font-size: 1rem;">
						<li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.7em; margin-bottom: 0.8em;"><span style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d6d4fa; flex-shrink: 0;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#d6d4fa"/><path d="M6 10.5L9 13.5L14 8.5" stroke="#23221F" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span style="line-height: 1.4;">Unlimited AI-powered surveys with dynamic summaries</span></li>
						<li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.7em; margin-bottom: 0.8em;"><span style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d6d4fa; flex-shrink: 0;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#d6d4fa"/><path d="M6 10.5L9 13.5L14 8.5" stroke="#23221F" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span style="line-height: 1.4;">4 wellbeing coaching conversations per employee/month (pooled)</span></li>
						<li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.7em; margin-bottom: 0.8em;"><span style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d6d4fa; flex-shrink: 0;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#d6d4fa"/><path d="M6 10.5L9 13.5L14 8.5" stroke="#23221F" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span style="line-height: 1.4;">Employee and manager dashboards</span></li>
						<li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.7em; margin-bottom: 0.8em;"><span style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d6d4fa; flex-shrink: 0;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#d6d4fa"/><path d="M6 10.5L9 13.5L14 8.5" stroke="#23221F" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span style="line-height: 1.4;">Slack / Microsoft Teams integration</span></li>
						<li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.7em; margin-bottom: 0.8em;"><span style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d6d4fa; flex-shrink: 0;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#d6d4fa"/><path d="M6 10.5L9 13.5L14 8.5" stroke="#23221F" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span style="line-height: 1.4;">Culture-building tools</span></li>
						<li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.7em; margin-bottom: 0.8em;"><span style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%; background: #d6d4fa; flex-shrink: 0;"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="10" fill="#d6d4fa"/><path d="M6 10.5L9 13.5L14 8.5" stroke="#23221F" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span style="line-height: 1.4;">GDPR‑ready data protection</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
					<h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
						<span style="color: #3bb273; font-size: 1.2rem;">💳</span> Payment & Confirmation
					</h2>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
						Submitting this form is an expression of interest, not a confirmed booking. We'll be in touch to finalise the details and send you an invoice. Your pilot will officially begin once payment is received.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
					<h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; color: #222; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
						<span style="color: #3bb273; font-size: 1.2rem;">🔄</span> We may adapt the offer
					</h2>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
						To maximise impact, our team may make small changes — like opening up the offer to more companies or adjusting timelines slightly. However, all the proceeds will always go to Forever Projects.
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem; text-align: center;">
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #222; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
						<strong>Every dollar goes to Forever Projects</strong> to help women in Tanzania create lasting change for their families.
					</div>
					<div style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6;">
						Thank you for being part of something meaningful. <span style="font-size: 1.2rem;">💛</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<div style="height: 3.5rem;"></div>
</Layout>

<style>
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    padding-left: 1rem !important;
    padding-right: 1rem !important;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem !important;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem !important;
  }
}
</style> 